WEBVTT

00:02.680 --> 00:03.135
...and you clearly didn't trust me
to make the right decision.

00:03.400 --> 00:04.135
I was worried about you.

00:04.400 --> 00:06.335
You don't have to be worried
about me! I'm not a child.

00:07.240 --> 00:08.015
Can I help you?

00:08.960 --> 00:09.695
He doesn't know?

00:09.920 --> 00:10.615
It's my son.

00:10.840 --> 00:13.015
He is everything to me.
You understand?

00:14.160 --> 00:16.375
Elise, I found him.
I found Saban. He's alive...

00:21.920 --> 00:23.735
Dad...When you were
in charge of the case...

00:24.080 --> 00:25.975
...why did you ask me to
exclude the hotel L'Écrin...

00:26.680 --> 00:27.775
...from the Charlie
Moreau investigation?

00:28.040 --> 00:29.215
I had an informant there.

00:29.840 --> 00:32.855
We got eleven missing person reports
in the last twenty four hours...

00:33.200 --> 00:33.895
...all from Folkestone.

00:34.200 --> 00:36.815
The last one is a delivery driver.

00:37.120 --> 00:38.335
He was driving a meat truck.

